author: Shubh_Mit
text:
No one actually thinks Humane, Tab or Rewind will replace phones. 
Smart glasses can actually do this and that's what Seleste is building. 
We've already shipped 50 glasses to blind people https://t.co/zPjwpvLPU3

author: Shubh_Mit
text:
Mark talking about Smart Glasses being the best form for a smart assistant because it takes in audio and video from your perspective. 

Also means that it can augment what you see and hear which is hugely important and something only smart glasses can do
